Palau, Italy

The house is located in the center of Palau, a few steps from the main square and the harbor. It is a typical house of the place, with a large terrace overlooking the sea. The house is on two floors, with a large living room, kitchen, two bedrooms and two bathrooms. The house is equipped with all the comforts, including air conditioning, washing machine, dishwasher, TV, wi-fi, etc. The house is ideal for a family or a group of friends.
